text.en_US: Any luck learning how to mod the weather?
Not really. I can't seem to figure it out.
What about that guy that made it snow in Maroon Valley?
He got banned before I could ask him how he did it.
It's working! I figured out how to modify the weather!
Is that why it is raining...\! indoors?!
The PVP content in XPC was designed to be played with an end-game loadout (level 60+). \c[3]Level scaling\c[0] is available, however opponents will still have all elements and utilize level 3 arts.
